{"type":"answer","id":16051,"parentType":"question","parentId":3506,"uid":2115,"contents":"<b>某些人,跪的久了,就忘了站着的好处。</b><br>\n<br>\n正如鲁迅先生所说:做奴隶虽然不幸,但并不可怕,因为知道挣扎,毕竟还有挣脱的希望;若是从奴隶生活中寻出美来,赞叹、陶醉,就是万劫不复的奴才了!<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181015/1539593071645043.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181015/1539593071645043.gif\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181015/1539593071645043.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-10-15","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}